      propertyPath: m_text
      value: '1. In Edit mode, select the Pose Detector and, add your pose and any
        variants of that pose


        2. Add any rules to your pose. Rules allow
        you to add directions to joints. E.g. Palm facing World Up


        3. Enter
        Play Mode and recreate your selected pose


        4. The Pose Validator
        will update the color of each joint to signal whether it matches the pose.
        You will be notified when the whole pose is met'
